## Testing Performed

### Test Setup

Created sample test data:
- [sample_source.csv](file:///Users/kkrishna/Library/CloudStorage/OneDrive-InfobloxInc/PycharmProjects/infoblox-DE/1UniversalFramework/universal-validator/tests/data/sample_source.csv) - 5 rows of test data
- [sample_target.csv](file:///Users/kkrishna/Library/CloudStorage/OneDrive-InfobloxInc/PycharmProjects/infoblox-DE/1UniversalFramework/universal-validator/tests/data/sample_target.csv) - Same data with one intentional mismatch (age: 25 vs 26)

### Test Configuration

Created [test_validation.yaml](file:///Users/kkrishna/Library/CloudStorage/OneDrive-InfobloxInc/PycharmProjects/infoblox-DE/1UniversalFramework/universal-validator/config/test_validation.yaml) for local testing without Redshift dependency.

### Expected Test Results

When running the test validation:
- ✅ Record count: PASS (5 rows in both)
- ✅ Column count: PASS (5 columns in both)
- ✅ Duplicate check: PASS (no duplicates)
- ✅ Null check: PASS (no nulls)
- ✅ Empty string check: PASS (no empty strings)
- ❌ Data validation: FAIL (1 mismatch in 'age' column for id=2)

